reviewText: In volume 2 of season 3 of UFO Ultramaiden Valkyrie, we get close to the wedding and we also meet Nesty (who was previously seen at the end of season 1). As for the wedding, well, that will have to wait until season 4. Like all the other volumes in the series, this one did not disappoint, however the only downside was Laine's time-travel adventure.
The funny part is the disfuncational family of Val,s and how they both try to deal with them.
